<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
  <title>NoSQL Injection Example</title>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
</head>

<body>
  <p>COSC3060 NoSQL Injection Demo</p>

  <p>A few things to test:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>Login as user 'admin' with password 'secret'</li>
    <li>Login as user 'admin' with password <code>'{"$gt":""}'</code></li>
    <li>Repeat but now using a API client, such as Postman</li>
    <li>Repeat with prepared statements checkbox enabled</li>
    <li>Login as user 'john' with password 'nodejs' (it's broken, you will fix it in the activity class).</li>
  </ul>

  <form>
    <div class="form-group" method="POST" action="/">
      <label for="username">Username:</label>
      <input type="text" name="username" id="username" value="admin">
    </div>
    <div class="form-group">
      <label for="password">Password:</label>
      <input type="password" name="password" id="password" value="">
    </div>
    <div class="form-group">
      <label for="secured">Enable secured:</label>
      <input type="checkbox" id="secured" name="secured">
    </div>
    <button type="submit" name="login">Login</button>
  </form>

  <script src="script.js"></script>
</body>

</html>